title: Five New Playoff Teams for 2019 with NFL SuperFriends (Football 8/8)
description:
Will Brinson, John Breech, Ryan Wilson and Sean Wagner-McGough break down the latest news and notes around the NFL, including the Cowboys losing Robert Quinn and how it might affect their start (6:00), if LeSean McCoy is 'the man' in Buffalo (15:30), whether Jameis Winston can become a Charlie Checkdown (21:30) and Damien Williams return to the Chiefs (27:30). Then the guys look at five teams who missed the playoffs last year that will make it in 2019 (30:00).
